'desc': [u'

Sunbaby Bath Tub with Music (Light Blue) Price: Rs.1299

Bathing is one of the regular activities of a baby and needs to be made a fun and exciting process so that the baby can enjoy it and looks forward to it. The Sunbaby Bath Tub is a cute
column14:
which interests and entertains the baby while he is having a bath.

This Musical Bath Tub from Sunbaby can be used for both boys and girls and is ideal for babies belonging to the age group of 0 to 2 years. The Soft Grip on the side of this bath tub ensures a comfortable and safe bath for the baby without causing any harm to his soft skin. The dimensions of this baby bath tub are 79 x 28 x 50 cm and it weighs 0.5 kg. The insides of this bath tub are imprinted with animal characters and there is a soap case provided for increased feasibility in the usage of this bath tub.
